data.name: sqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [Client] SET [FullName] = @FullName, [Number] = @Number, [Address] = @Address WHERE (([ID] = @Original_ID) AND ([FullName] = @Original_FullName) AND ([Number] = @Original_Number) AND ([Address] = @Original_Address)); SELECT ID, FullName, Number, Address FROM Client WHERE (ID = @ID)

data.name: sqlUpdateCommand2.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [Employees] SET [FullName] = @FullName, [Number] = @Number, [Address] = @Address WHERE (([ID] = @Original_ID) AND ((@IsNull_FullName = 1 AND [FullName] IS NULL) OR ([FullName] = @Original_FullName)) AND ((@IsNull_Number = 1 AND [Number] IS NULL) OR ([Number] = @Original_Number)) AND ((@IsNull_Address = 1 AND [Address] IS NULL) OR ([Address] = @Original_Address))); SELECT ID, FullName, Number, Address FROM Employees WHERE (ID = @ID)

data.name: sqlDeleteCommand2.CommandText
data.value: DELETE FROM [Employees] WHERE (([ID] = @Original_ID) AND ((@IsNull_FullName = 1 AND [FullName] IS NULL) OR ([FullName] = @Original_FullName)) AND ((@IsNull_Number = 1 AND [Number] IS NULL) OR ([Number] = @Original_Number)) AND ((@IsNull_Address = 1 AND [Address] IS NULL) OR ([Address] = @Original_Address)))

data.name: sqlSelectCommand3.CommandText
data.value: SELECT Contract.ID, Contract.ReturnTime, Contract.TimeOfIssue, Contract.IDClient, Contract.IDEmployees, Contract.Status, Contract.IDCars, Client.FullName, Employees.FullName AS Expr3, Cars.CarBrand FROM Contract INNER JOIN Client ON Contract.IDClient = Client.ID INNER JOIN Employees ON Contract.IDEmployees = Employees.ID INNER JOIN Cars ON Contract.IDCars = Cars.ID

data.name: sqlInsertCommand3.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [Cars] ([CarBrand], [Price], [CarMileage], [GosNomer], [GodVipuska], [NalichieAuto]) VALUES (@CarBrand, @Price, @CarMileage, @GosNomer, @GodVipuska, @NalichieAuto); SELECT ID, CarBrand, Price, CarMileage, GosNomer, GodVipuska, NalichieAuto FROM Cars WHERE (ID = SCOPE_IDENTITY())
